    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0057-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.11" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">九層の楼閣も</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.12" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">土を積み重ねることから始まり、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.13" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">千里の道も</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.14" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">足元の一歩から始まる。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.15" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">作為的に何かをしようとする者はそれを失敗し、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.16" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">執着する者はそれを失う。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.17" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">それゆえ聖人は無為であり、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.18" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">だから失敗することがなく、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.19" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">執着しないので、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.20" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">失うこともない。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.21" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">人々が事に携わる時、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.22" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">いつももう少しで完成するというところで失敗する。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.23" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">だから、終わりを慎むことを始めのようにすれば、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.24" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">失敗することはない。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.25" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">それゆえ聖人は欲しないことを欲し、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.26" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">手に入れにくい珍しい物を貴ばず、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.27" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">学ばないことを学び、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.28" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">多くの人々が過ちを犯すところを繰り返す。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.29" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">万物の自然なあり方を助け、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_064-1a.30" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">あえて何かをしようとはしない。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.1" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.3-h" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">第六十五章</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.3" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">昔、道をよく行った者は、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.4" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">民を賢くしようとしたのではなく、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.5" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">むしろ愚かにしようとしたのである。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.6" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">民が治めにくいのは、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.7" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">その知恵が多いからである。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.8" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">だから、知恵によって国を治めれば、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.9" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">国を害することになり、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.10" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">知恵によって国を治めなければ、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.11" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">国の幸せとなる。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.12" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">常にこの両者を知っているのは、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.13" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">すなわち模範となるやり方である。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_065-1a.14" xml:lang="ja" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-04-24T16:34:02.052+09:00">常に模範となるやり方を知り、</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
